(6906,	1182,	'features',	'Through the <strong>planning/aule</strong> portal, authorized users can:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>view the <strong>calendar of scheduled events and activities</strong> taking place in classrooms;</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>book classrooms and rooms</strong> for lectures, seminars, exams, meetings, and other institutional purposes;</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>check the real-time availability</strong> of spaces.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe interface allows for quick verification of available rooms and integrated management of booking requests, streamlining the coordination of teaching and institutional events.'),
(6909,	1182,	'requirements',	'Access to the platform i<strong>s reserved for authorized users</strong> with institutional credentials.\r\n\r\nPlanning <strong>does not allow booking of spaces for personal or individual use</strong>. In particular, it cannot be used to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>access administrative <strong>offices</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>book seats in the <strong>library, canteen, study rooms</strong>, or <strong>shared spaces</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor these purposes, please use the dedicated platform spazi\r\n\r\nAdditionally, for students and faculty wishing to view the course calendar or book a seat for in-person lectures, the <strong>Agenda Web platform</strong> and <strong>School mobile app</strong> (available on smartphones and tablets) are available.'),
(6912,	1182,	'get_started',	'To access the classroom booking system:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Go to planning/aule</li>\r\n 	<li>Log in using your credentials</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf authorized, you will be able to view and manage available room bookings'),
