(7197,	1218,	'features',	'Through the platform, <strong>users can book</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>workstations for library consultation</li>\r\n 	<li>offices and temporary workspaces</li>\r\n 	<li>common rooms and shared spaces</li>\r\n 	<li>laboratories</li>\r\n 	<li>study rooms (synchronized with the Planning system used for course and event scheduling)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Cannot be booked</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>seat reservations for in-person classes  (see Agenda Web)</li>\r\n 	<li>classroom bookings for teaching activities (courses, exams) or meetings (room booking platform)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;'),
