(1344,	3,	'2025-07-30 08:06:30',	'2025-07-30 08:06:30',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before contacting technical support directly, we kindly ask you to follow these steps:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Check the FAQs</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Answers to the most common issues are available in the FAQ section and can help you solve many problems on your own.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Review the documentation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The technical documentation and user guides are constantly updated and contain detailed information on procedures, configurations, and available tools.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If, after consulting the resources above, you haven\'t found a solution to your issue, you can contact our support team through one of the following channels:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Phone:</strong> +39 050 6133533</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:helpdesk@sns.it\">helpdesk@sns.it</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The helpdesk is available Monday to Friday during office hours:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Morning:</strong> 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Afternoon:</strong> 2:00 PM – 5:00 PM</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you contact us by email, please include all useful information to help identify the issue, such as:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Your full name</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The type of device or service involved</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A brief but clear description of the issue</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Any error messages displayed</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>When the issue started occurring</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This information will help us provide faster and more effective support.<br>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Help Desk',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'1041-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2025-07-30 08:06:30',	'2025-07-30 08:06:30',	'',	1041,	'https://demoict.local/?p=1344',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
